[03:56] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'animation - where soft, squishy worlds are&nbsp; no longer puppeteered but are truly moving&nbsp;&nbsp; realistically. This isn’t just eye candy -&nbsp; it’s a glimpse of creatures that move with&nbsp;&nbsp; the richness of real life. Absolutely&nbsp; brilliant. What a time to be alive!'

